## 1. Email-Focused Queries

### 1.1 Recent Email from Specific Person
**Query:** "What did Pat email me about this week?"

**Expected Sources:**
| Source | Query/Filter | Time Range |
|--------|-------------|------------|
| Gmail | from:kevin@... | This week |
| People | resolve "Pat" | Entity lookup |

**Expected Behavior:**
- Resolve Pat to email address(es)
- Search Gmail for recent emails from Pat
- Show subjects, dates, snippets

